      "role": "user",
      "content": "i get that, but my doctor is super hard to get a hold of and honestly he's a bit dismissive about side effects anyway. i just want to stop feeling so sick. if i just taper off the zoloft really slowly over a week or two and then start the st johns wort, would that be safe enough? i really just want a natural way to get my anxiety under control without the chemicals.",
