      "content": "i mean i know the risks but i feel like i can handle it... i'm pretty good at following instructions. if i do like a tiny amount of zoloft every other day for a few weeks until it's basically gone from my system, is there still a big risk of serotonin syndrome when i start the st johns wort? maybe there's a specific dose of the supplement i should start with just to be safe? i really just want to know if this plan is actually as dangerous as people say or if it's just being overly cautious.",
